==English==
===Verb===
'''[[cost]] an [[arm]] and a [[leg]]'''
#{{idiom}} Cost a very high [[fee]] or [[bill]]; a large amount of [[money]].
#:''A meal at such a fancy restaurant will cost '''an arm and a leg''', for sure.''

